credit_line: Gift of Mr. and Mrs. Abraham M. Adler
title: Psyche Trying to Stab Sleeping Cupid
description: Set of scenic wallpaper "Les Amours de Psyche", consisting of 26 panels; "Psyche Surprises the Sleeping Cupid" is on e of twelve scenes inspired by the Jean de La Fontaine story, "Les Amours de Psyche et Cupidon (1669). The narrative required twelve hundred forty-five woodblocks for printing. The scene depicts Psyche trying to stab sleeping cupid.
name: Scenic- panel
